p]]\n\n|}\n\n===Personnel and sponsorships===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- \n! Team\n! Head coach\n! Captain\n! Kit manufacturer\n! Shirt sponsor\n|-\n|Adria Oil \u0160krljevo\n|{{flagicon|CRO}} [[Damir Rajkovi\u0107]]\n|\n|GBT \n|Renault RB Auto / Metis d.o.o.\n|-\n|Alkar\n|{{flagicon|CRO}} [[Damir Mila\u010di\u0107]] \n|\n|[[Jako]] \n|IDS \u0160ibenik\n|-\n|Cibona\n|{{flagicon|BIH}} [[Ivan Veli\u0107]]\n|{{flagicon|CRO}} [[Marin Rozi\u0107]]\n|Visual\n|[[Erste Group|Erste Bank]] \n|-\n|Dubrava Furnir\n|{{flagicon|CRO}} [[Vladimir Krsti\u0107 (basketball)|Vladimir Krsti\u0107]]\n|\n|[[Legea]] \n|\n|-\n|Gorica\n|{{flagicon|CRO}} [[Josip Sesar]]\n|\n|Sportika\n|Mati\u0107 Tech Cut\n|-\n|Hermes Analitica\n|{{flagicon|CRO}} [[Gordan Zadravec]]\n|\n|[[Adidas]] \n|Orlando\n|-\n|Sonik Puntamika\n|{{flagicon|CRO}} [[\u0160ime Kraljevi\u0107]]\n|\n|[[Adidas]] \n|Sonik\n|-\n|Split\n|{{flagicon|CRO}} [[Ivica Skelin]]\n|{{flagicon|CRO}} [[Mateo Ked\u017eo]]\n|[[Macron (sportswear)|Macron]] \n|Bobis\n|-\n|\u0160ibenka\n|{{flagicon|CRO}} [[Edi D\u017eelalija]]\n|{{flagicon|CRO}} [[Domagoj Ba\u0161i\u0107]]\n|[[Errea]]\n|[[Krka National Park|NP Krka]]\n|-\n|Vrijednosnice\n|{{flagicon|CRO}} [[Domagoj Kujund\u017ei\u0107]]\n|{{flagicon|CRO}} [[Nikola Turalija]]\n|[[Nike, Inc.|Nike]] \n|\n|-\n|Zabok\n|{{flagicon|CRO}} [[Ivan Tomas]]\n|\n|[[Joma]]\n|Terme Tuhelj\n|-\n|Zadar\n|{{flagicon|CRO}} [[Danijel Jusup]]\n|{{flagicon|CRO}} [[Ive Ivanov]]\n|Visual\n|Crodux / [[OTP Bank]] \n|}\n\n===Coaching changes===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Team !! Outgoing manager !! Date of vacancy !! Position in table !! Replaced with !! Date of appointment !! Ref.\n|-\n| [[KK Alkar|Alkar]] || {{flagicon|CRO}} [[Sr\u0111an Helbich]] || June 2019 || ''Pre-season'' || {{flagicon|CRO}} [[Damir Mila\u010di\u0107]] || 18 June 2019 ||\n|-\n| [[KK Hermes Analitica|Hermes Analitica]] || {{flagicon|CRO}} [[Zvonimir Mravak]] || August 2019 || ''Pre-season'' || {{flagicon|CRO}} [[Gordan Zadravec]] || Aug